Got my 2nd #COVID19 #vaccine Monday. Felt my immune system responding w chills/myalgias at 12-20h. Thought I had a fever (for the 1st time in 15y) but @DrLeslieKim wouldn’t let me count 99.1F as a fever...

But no better feeling than protecting family, friends, and patients. 💯 https://t.co/S1dWTtpNvJ
